Sure, here are some examples of sentences in Serbian that use the word "biljke" (plants) in different forms and positions:

1. *Biljke* su mi omiljeni ukras u stanu. (Plants are my favorite decoration in my apartment.)
2. Mnogo volim da gajim *biljke* u bašti. (I love growing plants in my garden.)
3. U ovoj prodavnici možete naći razne vrste *biljaka*. (In this store, you can find various types of plants.)
4. *Biljke* su vrlo važne za ekosistem. (Plants are very important for the ecosystem.)
5. On je botaničar i bavi se proučavanjem različitih *biljnih* vrsta. (He is a botanist and studies different plant species.)
6. Naša kompanija se bavi proizvodnjom i distribucijom *biljnih* preparata. (Our company is involved in the production and distribution of herbal supplements.)
7. Upravo sam posadio nekoliko *biljki* u saksijama. (I just planted a few plants in pots.)
8. *Biljke* na ovom području su prilagođene surovim klimatskim uslovima. (Plants in this area are adapted to harsh climate conditions.)

I hope this helps!